{{Top|leg}}
'''Sentience programming''' or '''artificial sentience'''<ref name="CFTD">''[[Cynabar's Fantastic Technology: Droids]]''</ref> [[Metaprogramming|allowed]] a [[Droid/Legends|droid]] to [[Artificial intelligence/Legends|think]], feel, and value its own life. Such programming was gifted to [[IG-88A/Legends|IG-88]], who continued to give it to other droids that he recruited into his [[IG-88's Droid Army|army]]. This programming was the reason why [[Droid rights/Legends|droid rights]] sympathizers tried to free them from their "forced servitude", and was the highest level of autonomy a droid could attain.

